<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Automation Order</title>
</head>
<body>
  <p>Dear Supplier,</p>

    <ul>
        <li><strong>Warehouse:</strong> {{warehouseDetailData.warehouse.name}}</li>
        <li><strong>Address:</strong> {{warehouseDetailData.warehouse.address}}</li>
        <li><strong>Phone:</strong> {{warehouseDetailData.warehouse.phone}}</li>
    </ul>

  <p>We would like to inform you that the following warehouse requires a restock of the product listed below:</p>

    <table border="1" cellpadding="8" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; max-width: 600px;">
        <thead>
            <tr style="background-color: #f2f2f2;">
            <th align="left">Product Name</th>
            <th align="left">Quantity to Restock</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr>
            <td>{{warehouseDetailData.product.name}}</td>
            <td>{{warehouseDetailData.product.orderStock}}</td>
            </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>

  <p>Please proceed with the delivery at your earliest convenience to ensure uninterrupted supply.</p>

  <p>Thank you for your cooperation.</p>

  <p>Best regards,<br>
  Warehouse Management System</p>
</body>
</html>
